\c 2
\s Indumiso kaHana
\p
\v 1 UHana wasekhuleka esithi:
\p Inhliziyo yami iyathokoza eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + Luka 1.46-53. Hlab. 5.11. 9.2.\x*. Uphondo lwami luphakanyisiwe eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + Hlab. 75.10. 89.17,24. 92.10. 112.9. 148.14.\x*. Umlomo wami wenziwe banzi phezu kwezitha zami, ngoba ngiyajabula ngosindiso lwakho\x + Hlab. 9.14. 13.5. 20.5. 35.9.\x*.
\v 2 Kakho ongcwele njengeN\nd kosi\x + Eks. 15.11.\x*\nd*, ngoba kakho ngaphandle kwakho\x + Dute. 4.35.\x*; futhi kalikho idwala \add eli\add*njengoNkulunkulu wethu\x + Dute. 32.31.\x*.
\v 3 Lingabe lisakhuluma ngokuzigqaja lokuzigqaja, kungaphumi ukuziqakisa emlonyeni wenu; ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* inguNkulunkulu wolwazi, lezenzo zilinganiswa yiyo\x + Mal. 3.13. Juda 15.\x*.
\v 4 Idandili lamaqhawe lephukile, kodwa abakhubekileyo babhince amandla\x + Hlab. 37.15. 46.9. 76.3.\x*.
\v 5 Ababesuthi baziqatshisile ngesinkwa, lababelambile kabase\add njalo\x + Luka 1.53. Hlab. 34.10.\x*\add*, kwaze kwathi oyinyumba uzele abayisikhombisa\x + Hlab. 68.6. 113.9. Isa. 54.1.\x*, lolabantwana abanengi uphele amandla\x + Jer. 15.9.\x*.
\v 6 IN\nd kosi\nd* iyabulala njalo iyaphilisa, iyehlisela engcwabeni njalo yenyuse\x + Dute. 32.39.\x*.
\v 7 IN\nd kosi\nd* ipha ubuyanga, njalo iyanothisa\x + Eks. 15.9. Jobe 1.21.\x*; iyehlisela phansi, njalo iphakamise\x + Hlab. 75.7. Jobe 5.11.\x*.
\v 8 Iyamphakamisa umyanga ethulini, imphakamisa oswelayo enqunjini yomquba\x + Hlab. 113.7,8. Luka 1.52. Dan. 4.17.\x*, ukuze i\add ba\add*hlalise leziphathamandla, ibadlise ilifa lesihlalo sobukhosi sodumo\x + Jobe 36.7.\x*; ngoba insika zomhlaba zingezeN\nd kosi\nd*, ibekile ilizwe phezu kwazo\x + Jobe 38.4,5,6. Hlab. 24.2. 102.25. 104.5.\x*.
\v 9 Izagcina inyawo zabangcwele bayo\x + Hlab. 121.3. Zaga 3.26. Hlab. 91.11.\x*, kodwa ababi bazathuliswa emnyameni; ngoba umuntu kayikunqoba ngamandla.
\v 10 Abalwa leN\nd kosi\nd* bazaphahlazwa\x + Hlab. 2.9.\x*; izaduma phezu kwabo isemazulwini\x + 7.10. Hlab. 18.13. 2 Sam. 22.14.\x*; iN\nd kosi\nd* izakwahlulela imikhawulo yomhlaba, inike inkosi yayo amandla\x + Hlab. 96.10,13. 98.9.\x*, iphakamise uphondo logcotshiweyo wayo\x + 2.1.\x*.
\v 11 UElkana waya eRama endlini yakhe\x + 1.19.\x*. Lomfana wayekhonza iN\nd kosi\nd* phambi kukaEli umpristi\x + 2.18. 3.1.\x*.
\s Ububi bamadodana kaEli
\p
\v 12 Amadodana kaEli ayengabantwana bakaBheliyali\x + 1.3. Dute. 13.13.\x*; kawayazanga-ke iN\nd kosi\x + Hlu. 2.10.\x*\nd*.
\v 13 Njalo umkhuba wabapristi labantu wawu\add nje\add*; wonke umuntu ohlaba umhlatshelo, kube sekufika inceku yompristi, inyama isaphekiwe, ilefologwe elencijo ezintathu esandleni sayo,
\v 14 ihlabe ngayo edengezini, loba egedleleni, loba ebhodweni, loba embizeni; konke ifologwe ekukhuphayo umpristi wayezithathela khona\x + Levi 7.30-34. Dute. 18.3.\x*. Benze njalo kuIsrayeli wonke ofika lapho eShilo.
\v 15 Njalo engakatshisi amahwahwa, inceku yompristi ifike ithi emuntwini ohlabayo: Letha inyama yokosela umpristi, ngoba kayikuthatha kuwe inyama ephekiweyo, kodwa eluhlaza\x + Levi 3.3,4,5,16. 7.23,25,31.\x*.
\v 16 Uba lowomuntu esithi kuyo: Kabatshise lokutshisa amahwahwa khathesi, ubusuzithathela njengokuthanda komphefumulo wakho; ibisisithi kuye: Hatshi, \add ngi\add*nika khathesi; uba kungenjalo, ngizayithatha ngamandla.
\v 17 Ngakho isono samajaha saba sikhulu kakhulu phambi kweN\nd kosi\x + Gen. 6.11.\x*\nd*; ngoba abantu badelela umnikelo weN\nd kosi\x + Mal. 2.8.\x*\nd*.
\p
\v 18 Kodwa uSamuweli wayekhonza phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* engumfana\x + 2.11.\x* ebhince \w i-efodi\w** yelembu elicolekileyo\x + Eks. 28.4. 2 Sam. 6.14. 1 Lan. 15.27. Levi 6.10.\x*.
\v 19 Futhi unina wayemenzela ijazana, amphathele lona umnyaka ngomnyaka ekwenyukeni kwakhe lomkakhe ukuyahlaba umhlatshelo womnyaka\x + 1.3.\x*.
\p
\v 20 UEli wasebabusisa oElkana lomkakhe, wathi: IN\nd kosi\nd* ikunike inzalo ngalowesifazana endaweni yesicelo esicelwe eN\nd kosi\nd*ni. Basebesiya endaweni yabo\x + Nani 6.23. Gen. 14.19.\x*.
\v 21 IN\nd kosi\nd* isimhambele uHana, wasethatha isisu, wazala amadodana amathathu lamadodakazi amabili\x + Gen. 21.1.\x*. Umfana uSamuweli wasekhula eleN\nd kosi\x + 2.26. Hlu. 13.24.\x*\nd*.
\p
\v 22 Kodwa uEli wayesemdala kakhulu; wakuzwa konke amadodana akhe akwenza kuIsrayeli wonke\x + 2.13-16.\x*, lokuthi ayelala labesifazana ababuthana emnyango wethente lenhlangano.
\v 23 Wasesithi kuwo: Lenzelani izinto ezinje? Ngoba ngiyezwa ngabo bonke abantu ngezenzo zenu ezimbi.
\v 24 Hatshi, madodana ami; ngoba kakusumbiko omuhle engiwuzwayo ukuthi lenza abantu beN\nd kosi\nd* baphambuke.
\v 25 Uba umuntu esona komunye, abahluleli bazamahlulela\x + Eks. 21.6. 22.8,9,28. Eks. 12.12.\x*; kodwa uba umuntu esona eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, ngubani ozamlamulela? Kodwa kawalalelanga ilizwi likayise; ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* yayifuna ukuwabulala\x + Josh. 11.20. Zaga 15.10.\x*.
\v 26 Umfana uSamuweli waseqhubeka ekhula\x + 2.21. Gen. 26.13. 2 Lan. 17.12.\x*, ethandeka kubo bobabili iN\nd kosi\nd* labantu\x + Luka 2.52. Zaga 3.4. Seb. 24.16. Roma 14.18.\x*.
\s Ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* lokugwetshwa kwendlu kaEli
\p
\v 27 Kwasekufika umuntu kaNkulunkulu kuEli\x + 1 Kho. 13.1. Hlu. 13.6.\x*, wathi kuye: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Ngabonakaliswa lokubonakaliswa yini kuyo indlu kayihlo beseGibhithe endlini kaFaro\x + Eks. 4.14,27.\x*?
\v 28 Ngamkhetha yini kuzo zonke izizwe zakoIsrayeli ukuthi abe ngumpristi wami\x + Eks. 28.1-4. Nani 18.1,7.\x*, anikele elathini lami, atshise impepha, agqoke i-efodi phambi kwami\x + 14.3. 22.18.\x*? Ngayinika yini indlu kayihlo yonke iminikelo yabantwana bakoIsrayeli eyenziwe ngomlilo\x + Levi 2.3,10. 6.16. 7.7,8,34. 10.14,15. Nani 5.9,10. 18.8-19.\x*?
\v 29 Kungani likhahlela imihlatshelo yami leminikelo yami\x + Dute. 32.15.\x* engiyilayileyo \add e\add*ndli\add ni yami\x + 2.32. Dute. 26.15. 33.27. 1 Lan. 4.41. Hlab. 26.8. 68.5. Dute. 12.5,6.\x*\add*, njalo uhlonipha amadodana akho okwedlula mina, ngokuzikhuluphalisa ngekhethelo leminikelo yonke kaIsrayeli, abantu bami?
\v 30 Ngakho iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli ithi: Ngathi lokuthi: Indlu yakho lendlu kayihlo zizahamba phambi kwami kuze kube nininini\x + Eks. 27.21. 29.5.\x*; kodwa khathesi ithi iN\nd kosi\nd*: Kakube khatshana lami\x + Jer. 18.9,10.\x*; ngoba abangihloniphayo ngizabahlonipha\x + Hlab. 91.14.\x*, labangidelelayo bazakweyiswa\x + Mal. 2.9.\x*.
\v 31 Khangela, insuku ziyeza engizaquma ngazo ingalo yakho lengalo yendlu kayihlo, kungabi khona ixhegu endlini yakho\x + 4.11,18,20. 22.18. 1 Kho. 2.27.\x*.
\v 32 Njalo uzabona ukuhlupheka kwendlu \add yami\add*, kuyo yonke impumelelo ezayenzela uIsrayeli; njalo kakuyikuba lexhegu endlini yakho zonke izinsuku\x + 2.33. Zek. 8.4.\x*.
\v 33 Lowo-ke owakho engingayikumquma asuke elathini lami uzakuba ngowokuqeda amehlo akho, lokudabula umphefumulo wakho; lakho konke ukwanda kwendlu yakho kuzakufa kusebudodeni.
\v 34 Lalokhu kuzakuba yisiboniso kuwe okuzakwehlela amadodana akho womabili, kuHofini loPhinehasi\x + 1 Kho. 13.3.\x*; bobabili bazakufa ngasuku lunye\x + 4.11.\x*.
\v 35 Ngizazimisela umpristi othembekileyo; uzakwenza njengokusenhliziyweni yami lemphefumulweni wami\x + 1 Kho. 2.35.\x*. Njalo ngizamakhela indlu eqinileyo\x + 25.28. 1 Kho. 11.38. 2 Sam. 7.11,27.\x*; uzahamba-ke phambi kogcotshiweyo wami zonke izinsuku\x + 2 Sam. 22.51. Hlab. 18.50. Hlab. 89.20.\x*.
\v 36 Kuzakuthi-ke wonke oseleyo endlini yakho uzakuza akhothame kuye ngenxa yembadalo yesiliva leqebelengwana lesinkwa, athi: Ake ungibeke kwesinye sezikhundla zompristi ukuze ngidle ucezu lwesinkwa\x + 10.3. Eks. 29.23. Hlu. 8.5. Zaga 6.26.\x*.
